### BlahTime
BlahTime is a client for XMPP based on Qt5 & Qt Quick2. It supports Windows, Linux, Mac, Symbian, Meego, Android and so on.  

### Support or Contact
If you have any advice or problem, please send an email to email@blahtime.com thank you.
